<p>流通是Openflows的活态层：随条件变化而在系统中当下流动之物。三种形式，各具不同的稳定程度与关注焦点。</p>

<section class="currency-section">
  <div class="currency-section-header">
    <h2>流</h2>
    <span class="entry-count muted">{{ collections.zh_currents.length }} 条目</span>
  </div>
  <p class="meta">暂时性的运动：来自开源AI生态系统的信号、张力与早期模式。</p>
  <ul class="currency-list">
    {% for item in collections.zh_currents %}
      {% if loop.index0 < 3 %}
      <li>
        <a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.data.title }}</a>
        {% if item.data.abstract %}<p class="item-abstract">{{ item.data.abstract }}</p>{% endif %}
        <div class="item-meta">
          <span class="muted">{{ item.date | readableDate }}</span>
        </div>
      </li>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
  <p><a href="/zh/currency/currents/">查看全部流 →</a></p>
</section>

